Summary: Photos of elongated, multi-colored, illuminated objects
divs: Sighting DetailsI was photographing the night sky using a Canon G9 and Sunpak 544 flash. Visible among the photos was the first object, taken about 8:52pm. Nine hours later I returned for another round of photos and captured the second object at 6:00am. The photos enclosed have been cropped and enlarged with Photoshop. The original photos, plus many others, are available for expert analysis.
